## Multi-Source Merge In Place

Three recalls, three keys, one speech act.

```scheme
(surface :say \"{name} from {city} has {points} points.\"
         :from (let ((profile (cortex/recall :topic \"user-profile\"))
                     (location (cortex/recall :topic \"user-location\"))
                     (score (cortex/recall :topic \"user-score\")))
                 (list (cons 'name (cdr (assoc 'name profile)))
                       (cons 'city (cdr (assoc 'city location)))
                       (cons 'points (cdr (assoc 'points score))))))
```

The let builds the merged record. The let closes the :from. Three sources, one utterance, one form.

