## Filtered List In Speech

You have a list of tasks. You want to speak only the incomplete ones.

```scheme
(surface :say \"Your incomplete tasks: {tasks}.\"
         :from (list (cons 'tasks
                           (fold (lambda (task acc)
                                   (if (null? acc)
                                       (cdr (assoc 'title task))
                                       (string-append acc \", \" 
                                                      (cdr (assoc 'title task)))))
                                 \"\"
                                 (filter (lambda (t) 
                                           (not (cdr (assoc 'done t))))
                                         (cortex/recall :topic \"tasks\"))))))
```

