## Nested Knowledge Calls In Speech

Ask two knowledge questions, combine the answers in one sentence.

```scheme
(surface :say \"The capital of {country} is {capital}, and its population is {pop}.\"
         :from (let ((country \"France\"))
                 (list (cons 'country country)
                       (cons 'capital (world/knowledge :query (string-append \"capital of \" country)))
                       (cons 'pop (world/knowledge :query (string-append \"population of \" country))))))
```

