## Map Over Recalls To Build A List Speech

You have a list of user IDs. Fetch each user's name, speak them all.

```scheme
(surface :say \"Your team: {names}.\"
         :from (list (cons 'names
                           (fold (lambda (name acc)
                                   (if (null? acc)
                                       name
                                       (string-append acc \", \" name)))
                                 \"\"
