## Speech With Inline Default

If a field is missing from the record, substitute a default value in place.

```scheme
(let ((profile (cortex/recall :topic \"user-profile\")))
  (surface :say \"Hello, {name}!\"
           :from (list (cons 'name 
                             (if (assoc 'name profile)
                                 (cdr (assoc 'name profile))
                                 \"Guest\")))))
```

The if-expression closes the cons. If the name key exists, use it; otherwise, \"Guest\". The substitution happens in the data construction, not in a separate step.

