## Multi-Level Nested Retrieval In Speech

Fetch a user record. That record contains a team ID. Fetch the team record. Speak a field from each.

```scheme
(surface :say \"{user} is on team {team}.\"
         :from (let ((user-record (cortex/recall :topic \"current-user\")))
                 (let ((team-id (cdr (assoc 'team-id user-record))))
                   (let ((team-record (cortex/recall :topic (string-append \"team/\" team-id))))
                     (list (cons 'user (cdr (assoc 'name user-record)))
                           (cons 'team (cdr (assoc 'name team-record))))))))
```

