## Speech From A Fold Calculation

Sum a list of numbers, speak the total.

```scheme
(surface :say \"Your total score is {total} points.\"
         :from (list (cons 'total 
                           (fold + 0 
                                 (map (lambda (record) 
                                        (cdr (assoc 'points record)))
                                      (cortex/recall :topic \"achievements\"))))))
```

The map extracts point values. The fold sums them. The fold closes the cons. The cons closes the :from. Aggregation and speech in one form.

