                  ((plus) \"You're on Plus. {limit} requests remaining.\")
                  ((pro) \"You're on Pro. Unlimited requests.\"))
           :from (cortex/recall :topic \"usage-stats\")))
```

The case-expression closes the template. The recall closes the :from. The :from closes the say. One form, three possible templates.

