## Speech With Multiple Inline Calculations

Calculate two derived values, speak both.

```scheme
(let ((total (cdr (assoc 'total (cortex/recall :topic \"order\"))))
      (tax-rate 0.08))
  (let ((tax (* total tax-rate))
